  card: {
    question: '<p>Percentages on properties such as *padding-top</p>\n<p>???</p>\n',
    answers: [
      {
        text: 'and *margin-top* are calculated based on the',
      },
      {
        text: 'width of the container.',
      },
      {
        text: 'height of the container.',
      },
      {
        text: 'perimeter of the container.',
      },
      {
        text: 'area of the container.',
      },
    ],
    comment: '<p>Width percentage is intuitively calculated based on the width of the container.</p>\n<p>However, percentages on properties like <code>padding-top</code> and <code>margin-top</code> are also calculated based on the <em>width</em> of the container, rather than the height.</p>\n<pre><code class="language-css">div {\n  height: 100px;\n  width:  400px;\n  padding-left: 10%; /* = 40px */\n  padding-top: 50%;  /* = 200px */\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Another example:</p>\n<p><img src="%3C?xml%20version=%221.0%22%20encoding=%22UTF-8%22%20standalone=%22no%22?%3E%0A%3Csvg%20width=%22100%25%22%20height=%22auto%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20800%20310%22%0A%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20xmlns:xlink=%22http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink%22%20%20version=%221.2%22%20baseProfile=%22tiny%22%3E%0A%3Cdesc%3ECreated%20by%20HiQPdf%3C/desc%3E%0A%3Cdefs%3E%0A%3C/defs%3E%0A%3Cg%20fill=%22none%22%20stroke=%22black%22%20stroke-width=%221%22%20fill-rule=%22evenodd%22%20stroke-linecap=%22square%22%20stroke-linejoin=%22bevel%22%20%3E%0A%0A%3Cg%20fill=%22#000000%22%20fill-opacity=%221%22%20stroke=%22#000000%22%20stroke-opacity=%221%22%20stroke-width=%221%22%20stroke-linecap=%22square%22%20stroke-linejoin=%22miter%22%20stroke-miterlimit=%222%22%20transform=%22matrix%281,0,0,1,0,0%29%22%0A%3E%0A%3C/g%3E%0A%0A%3Cg%20fill=%22#000000%22%20fill-opacity=%221%22%20stroke=%22#000000%22%20stroke-opacity=%221%22%20stroke-width=%221%22%20stroke-linecap=%22square%22%20stroke-linejoin=%22miter%22%20stroke-miterlimit=%222%22%20transform=%22matrix%281,0,0,1,0,0%29%22%0A%3E%0A%3C/g%3E%0A%0A%3Cg%20fill=%22#000000%22%20fill-opacity=%221%22%20stroke=%22#000000%22%20stroke-opacity=%221%22%20stroke-width=%221%22%20stroke-linecap=%22square%22%20stroke-linejoin=%22miter%22%20stroke-miterlimit=%222%22%20transform=%22matrix%281,0,0,1,0,0%29%22%0A%3E%0A%3C/g%3E%0A%0A%3Cg%20fill=%22#596193%22%20fill-opacity=%221%22%20stroke=%22none%22%20transform=%22matrix%281,0,0,1,0,0%29%22%0A%3E%0A%3Cpath%20vector-effect=%22